Company Overview of Grupo Ferrer Internacional, S.A.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Grupo Ferrer Internacional, S.A. operates a pharmaceutical and chemical company. The company discovers, develops, manufactures, and markets active medicinal substances, diagnostics, new pharmaceutical forms, drug re-profiling, cell therapy, personalized medicine, new therapeutic targets, vaccines, galenic formulations, and food and feed additives. It offers pharmaceuticals in the fields of cardiology, central nervous system, dermatology, gastroenterology, metabolism, oncology, musculoskeletal system, paediatrics, pain management, and respiratory system; and consumer health products, such as dermocosmetics, sunscreens, food supplements, antilice products, insect repellants, over-the-counter m...
Grupo Ferrer Internacional, S.A. operates a pharmaceutical and chemical company. The company discovers, develops, manufactures, and markets active medicinal substances, diagnostics, new pharmaceutical forms, drug re-profiling, cell therapy, personalized medicine, new therapeutic targets, vaccines, galenic formulations, and food and feed additives. It offers pharmaceuticals in the fields of cardiology, central nervous system, dermatology, gastroenterology, metabolism, oncology, musculoskeletal system, paediatrics, pain management, and respiratory system; and consumer health products, such as dermocosmetics, sunscreens, food supplements, antilice products, insect repellants, over-the-counter medicines, and infant nutrition products. The company also provides personalized medicines; generic drugs; ingredients, excipients, intermediates, food ingredients, flavorings, sweeteners, animal nutrition, and nutraceuticals; and vaccines solutions for allergies. Grupo Ferrer Internacional, S.A. was formerly known as Laboratorios Ferrer, S.L. and changed its name to Grupo Ferrer Internacional, S.A. in 1975. The company was founded in 1959 and is based in Barcelona, Spain with pharmaceutical production plants in Barcelona and Murcia, Spain; and a logistics center in Girona, Spain.
Detailed Description


