About Tire Group International, LLC.
Since 1992, Tire Group International, LLC. has clearly established itself as one of the fastest growing companies in the worldwide wholesale distribution of tires. The company’s dedicated commitment to quality and sensitivity to customer satisfaction has set a standard for others to follow. TGI’s extensive inventory of over forty different brands of tires, including various brands of tubes and wheels, and several brands of tire repair products, clearly separates them from their competition.
