100% Quality Guaranteed Call Center



Multilingual Virtual Call Center for the Direct Response industry, Call center outsourcing, outsourced customer service and lead generation with native presence in over 29 countries. Get your international call center set up and running in less than a week at unbeatable low cost. Take advantage of our 20+ years of experience in call center outsourcing and state of the art communication infrastructure to give your business the international edge.







Multilingual Customer Service

Virtual multilingual call center which gives your business an international advantage and allows your customers to reach out to you at anytime, anywhere & in any language. Leverage the inbound contact to up sell to your existing customers and launch an outbound calling campaign to garner new sales leads…..



Read More 






Call Center Outsourcing

Get us to undertake the entire sales cycle for you, right from fresh lead generation thru to closing. Train us just once about your USPs and we percolate the knowledge to our global call center executives to deliver consistent high quality customer service which results in higher lead generation and lead conversion…..




Read More 






Customer Retention

Not just retain but up sell to your existing customers. We specialize in helping your customers explore your entire range of products or services, so that they can select and buy better. Don’t miss the opportunity to explain your offerings and increase your per customer revenue at a fraction of a cost of new customer acquisition…



Read More 






Direct Response

Grow your real time sales business thru our experienced direct response call center agents. Convert maximum number of inbound calls, emails and chats into business. Get your direct response call center up and running to scale up your revenue and increase your customer base across several countries and regions…




Read More 












Make Your Business Global

24/7 Multilingual Call Center To Increase Your Business and Reach Out To International Clients. Experienced native language speakers, direct response, boost your sales and secure customer retention.











